" Vertical diffs on current file or any git object SHA.
" :h fugitive-object helpers: @ aka HEAD, :% index version of <cfile>
nnoremap <silent><Leader>gd <cmd>Gvdiffsplit<CR>
nnoremap <Leader>gD :Gvdiffsplit<space>

